digiKam 2.5.0 - Release date: 2012-01-01

NEW FEATURES:

Libkdcraw : use internal libraw 0.14.4 to support new RAW camera :
            Canon S100, Fuji X10, Panasonic GX1, Samsung NX200, Sony NEX-7.

